snippet.title: Zones & Signature Buildings I Feature Highlights Ep 4 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
Ready to plop, plop, plop?🏗️

🏘️ Take a look at new & returning zoning tools, types, and options in Cities: Skylines II. 

🏭 Find out what makes Signature Buildings special and how you can elevate your city's neighborhoods using this brand-new feature. 🌆 

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.

Pre-Order Cities: Skylines II NOW!
